				<div class="thumbnail customStyle1">
					<a class="imageOverlayLink" href="http://www.functionmagazine.ca" target="_blank">
<img src="/content/dam/image-arts/giffunction4.gif" alt="Photo Program's Function Visual Art Annual"/>



<span class='sr-only'>, external link, opens in new window</span></a>
					 
						<div class="caption richtextContent">
